Question: Is the color of the towel different than the robe?

Reference Answer: no

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n433532.jpg

Original program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='towel')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='robe')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What color is the towel?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What color is the robe?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0}!= {ANSWER1} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
